    },
    {
      "block_id": "p10_b4",
      "translation": "Over the past century, AIA"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p10_b5",
      "translation": "has earned recognition across Asia for providing protection"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p10_b6",
      "translation": "to communities in need of our services,"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p10_b7",
      "translation": "which makes us proud."
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p10_b8",
      "translation": "Mr. Tse Sze-wing\nIndependent Non-Executive Chairman"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p10_b9",
      "translation": "During the COVID-19 pandemic,"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p10_b10",
      "translation": "our colleagues cared for the community and fulfilled their duties,"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p10_b11",
      "translation": "providing uninterrupted support to millions of customers"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p10_b12",
      "translation": "without interruption."
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p10_b13",
      "translation": "AIA has a long and storied history in Asia, successfully managing its business through various social upheavals and uncertain periods, earning an outstanding"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p10_b14",
      "translation": "reputation that reflects AIA's trustworthiness, resilience, and commitment to doing the right thing for stakeholders. Since early 2020, the COVID-19 pandemic has"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p10_b15",
      "translation": "created an increasingly complex business environment, with unprecedented shifts in political, macroeconomic, and capital market conditions. In this context,"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p10_b16",
      "translation": "AIA's financial strength and mission to \"help people live healthier, longer, better lives\" are more significant than ever. I sincerely thank all AIA"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p10_b17",
      "translation": "employees, agents, and partners who, despite facing the most severe challenges, continue to care for the community and dedicate themselves to supporting our customers,"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p10_b18",
      "translation": "their families, and our communities."
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p10_b19",
      "translation": "Due to COVID-19 control measures impacting new business sales, new business value declined to USD 2.765 billion. We quickly adopted"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p10_b20",
      "translation": "innovative digital tools to enhance operational efficiency, and with recent relaxation of restrictions, sales momentum recovered strongly and continued into early 2021."
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p10_b21",
      "translation": "New business value in the first two months of 2021 grew 15% compared to the same period last year."
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p10_b22",
      "translation": "After-tax operating profit grew 5% to USD 5.942 billion, with free surplus generated rising 7% to USD 5.843 billion, reflecting the high quality of our"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p10_b23",
      "translation": "recurring earnings sources. Embedded value equity reached a record USD 67.2 billion. As of December 31, 2020, the Group's local capital aggregation method coverage ratio was"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p10_b24",
      "translation": "374%, demonstrating our strong capital position and prudent financial management."
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p10_b25",
      "translation": "The Board recommends a final dividend of HKD 100.30 per share, an increase of 7.5%, reflecting our solid financial performance and the Board's continued confidence in the Group's"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p10_b26",
      "translation": "future prospects. This brings the full-year 2020 dividend to HKD 135.30 per share. The Board maintains AIA's long-standing prudent, sustainable,"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p10_b27",
      "translation": "and progressive dividend policy, enabling the Group to capture future growth opportunities while maintaining financial flexibility."
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p10_b28",
      "translation": "008\nAIA Group Limited"
    }
  ]
